Version 1.0
-----------
  * It is probably a good idea to save after each section (except the
    Dream section; you can probably make it through that again with
    little or no trouble :-)

  * If you're not a purist, you can cut the Maze section down
    considerably by using the gaspar spell (found in the Guild hall in
    Helistar's room--from Belboz's quarters go e -- s -- w).

    Then, in the room outside the maze learn fweep and gaspar instead
    of 3 fweeps, then gaspar me.  Then after you drop the scroll into
    the hole, wait for the Dorn to kill you.  You will be reincarnated
    back where you gaspar'd yourself.

  * There are of course lots of fun things you can do.  One highly
    amusing thing is to meef Belboz's morgia plant before leaving the
    Guild hall, then check out the last line in the game after you win
    :-)

